01:07:13.829 --> 01:07:18.166
<i>Crow catchers,</i>
<i>dead and gone...</i>
classics, classics!

01:07:19.769 --> 01:07:22.003
Hello, lamonica.

01:07:22.037 --> 01:07:24.472
Are you as thrilled
about this evening
as we are, sir?

01:07:24.507 --> 01:07:27.208
All preparations
proceeding apace,
mcgreavey?

01:07:27.243 --> 01:07:30.245
Macgibbon, sir,
and yes, they are.

01:07:30.279 --> 01:07:32.514
We could not possibly
have it more under control.

01:07:34.817 --> 01:07:36.351
Lacy?

01:07:36.385 --> 01:07:38.153
Lacy, no!

