phantom to pull off.

01:08:02.945 --> 01:08:04.979
Well, you know
he's gonna try
something like it.

01:08:05.014 --> 01:08:06.881
Come on.
Let's go warn Pete.

01:08:17.792 --> 01:08:20.261
Wait your turn!
Sorry, sir.

01:08:23.799 --> 01:08:25.934
All right,
maccarthy...
Macgibbon.

01:08:25.968 --> 01:08:27.502
Since you don't have any answers

01:08:27.536 --> 01:08:30.537
as to why our balloons
became water balloons,

01:08:30.573 --> 01:08:32.740
perhaps you can answer this.

01:08:32.774 --> 01:08:34.408
Who told you to remove

01:08:34.443 --> 01:08:37.912
the incredibly expensive
mayhem monster
from my roof?

01:08:41.317 --> 01:08:43.818
I didn't remove it, sir.

01:08:43.853 --> 01:08:45.185
It's up
there... Still.

01:08:45.220 --> 01:08:46.220
Exactly the way
you wanted it
to be.

01:08:46.255 --> 01:08:48.957
And I'm telling you,
that 10 minutes ago

01:08:48.991 --> 01:08:50.892
when I came in, it wasn't there!

01:08:50.926 --> 01:08:52.694
Pardon me!
Lamonica:
Whoa!

01:08:52.728 --> 01:08:58.299
Ah, Wolfgang. I am
simply stopping in
to say good-bye.

01:08:58.334 --> 01:09:01.069
Ms. Tory Hicks!

01:09:01.103 --> 01:09:03.304
The woman who
brought the tinsel
to tinseltown.

01:09:03.339 --> 01:09:04.973
Of course you know
Tyler jesseman.
Yes.

01:09:05.006 --> 01:09:06.447
Good-bye? What do
you mean, good-bye?

01:09:06.475 --> 01:09:08.142
Just because I call
my people cattle

01:09:08.176 --> 01:09:10.377
